 <!-- Introduction -->
 <!-- The introduction should start as shown: -->
 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of relationships between identifiers.
   </p>
   <example>
     "John Smith" is an identifier for the person known as "John Smith". "JS" is an abbreviation of "John Smith".
     Both "John Smith" and "JS" are identifiers assigned to the object representing the person and are related
     to each other to indicate that "JS" is an abbreviation of "John Smith".    
   </example>
 </purpose>

